Blessed Udoh (a mụrụ n'ọnwa Nọvemba n'afọ 1984) bụ nwafọ Naijiria na- ebu ibu arọ, na-asọ mpi na katịgori nke 48kg otu na-anọchite anya Naịjirịa na asọmpi mba ụwa.
O sonyere na 2004 Summer Olympics n'ihe omume 48kg
Ọ sọrọ mpi na asọmpi nke mba ụwa, na nso nso a na 2001 World Weightlifting Championship
Udoh ritere ihe nrite 3 n’ime katigori 48kg nke ụmụ nwaanyị na 2007 All-Africa Games, ma nwale a nwalere ya gosiri na ọ gbara ọgwụ ike mgbe asọmpi ahụ gasịrị
